snippet.title: Amber Heard DENIED by Judge as NOTHING Changes For Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
More About Johnny Depp and Amber Heard...
A Virginia judge declined to sanction Depp’s attorney over the disclosure of a deposition from the actor’s former agent that purportedly detailed his substance abuse and anger during the time he was married to actress Amber Heard.
